      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade specimen features a high-revving, naturally aspirated V8 powerplant that maintains precise factory tolerances and exceptional throttle response. The dual-clutch transmission delivers seamless, lightning-fast gear changes, paired with a sophisticated limited-slip differential for superior lateral grip and power delivery. Every suspension bushing and damper remains taut, ensuring razor-sharp turn-in and optimal chassis rigidity. The undercarriage is pristine, showing no signs of oxidation or fluid weeping, while the exterior finish retains its deep, factory luster. This is a mechanically flawless example for the discerning enthusiast seeking a turn-key performance icon.",
