      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the absolute pinnacle of its class, presented in true showroom condition. The exterior features a flawless factory paint finish with a deep, mirror-like luster, completely free of rock chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, reflecting its meticulous history of climate-controlled garage storage. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule; the premium leather upholstery remains supple and matte, showing no signs of bolster wear or creasing, while the high-tech dashboard and infotainment systems still have their factory-fresh responsiveness. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy, documented by a comprehensive service portfolio. The engine bay is immaculate, and the driving experience is characterized by whisper-quiet operation and razor-sharp handling that feels identical to the day it was first delivered. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire an essentially new vehicle at a used-market value.",
